  {
    "client_msg_id": "18f7a7d7-5270-407b-8cdb-6d878cc28810",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "<@UEGFXUK3M> Glamorous Toolkit is a graphical and tooling environment. A Pharo system is made of a VM and image. An image offers the language and runtime, and the environment. Glamorous Toolkit offers an alternative environment, which is half of the image, and arguably, what makes a Smalltalk system special.\n\nIn fact, the Pharo distribution already ships the first generation of the Glamorous Toolkit since four years. The new generation that you see at <http://gtoolkit.com|gtoolkit.com> is based on a complete new implementation on top of a new graphical stack that has some unique properties and includes a highly flexible and dynamic text editor.",
    "user": "UE1JQM9HQ",
